      "sha256": "194fe6b953b711be7d8c1526c1ba3ba15e6983533bcaa73f758e68d1d57e56bf",
      "transparent": false,
      "alt_text": "The shock still hasn't worn off. I've cried, laughed, sung, and felt scared all at once.\n\nThis book lived inside me for years, most of the time hidden. Writing it meant returning to experiences no one should endure, trying to understand what happened, and finding language for the parts of myself I had folded away.\n\nI wanted to take a moment to acknowledge the women who gave me the strength and support to write this and put it before an editor. Without their gentle encouragement, this book would not be here today.\n\nThis story erupted from me, demanding to be told, even when I tried to ignore it.",
      "embedded_text": [
        "The shock still hasn't worn off. I've cried, laughed, sung, and felt scared all at once.",
        "This book lived inside me for years, most of the time hidden. Writing it meant returning to experiences no one should endure, trying to understand what happened, and finding language for the parts of myself I had folded away.",
        "I wanted to take a moment to acknowledge the women who gave me the strength and support to write this and put it before an editor. Without their gentle encouragement, this book would not be here today.",
        "This story erupted from me, demanding to be told, even when I tried to ignore it."
      ],
      "clickable": false,
      "destination": null,
      "position_in_assembly_sequence": 10
